# Rise Of Civilization Project Rules

## Docker Reset Workflow
- **After every change**, run `pnpm docker:reset`. This applies to all agents (including /coder) and all changes.
- Treat this as mandatory, not optional. Run it yourself after making changes.
- Only skip if the user explicitly says "don't reset Docker" or "skip docker reset".

## Authoritative Rules
Full project rules live in `docs/project-rules.md`. Read before major implementation.
